query.esql:
FROM logs-corelight.various*
| WHERE event.dataset == "ssh"
| LIMIT 10000
| STATS COUNT() by source.ip, destination.ip, ssh.hassh, ssh.hasshServer 
| RENAME source.ip as `Source IP`,ssh.hassh as `HASSH Client`, destination.ip as `Destination IP`, ssh.hasshServer as `HASSH Server`, `COUNT()` as `Total Events`
| SORT `Total Events` DESC
| LIMIT 5
| KEEP `Source IP`, `HASSH Client`,`Destination IP`, `HASSH Server`, `Total Events`

FROM logs-corelight.various*
| WHERE event.dataset == "ssh"
| LIMIT 10000
| STATS COUNT() by source.ip, destination.ip, ssh.hassh, ssh.hasshServer 
| RENAME source.ip as `Source IP`,ssh.hassh as `HASSH Client`, destination.ip as `Destination IP`, ssh.hasshServer as `HASSH Server`, `COUNT()` as `Total Events`
| SORT `Total Events` DESC
| LIMIT 5
| KEEP `Source IP`, `HASSH Client`,`Destination IP`, `HASSH Server`, `Total Events`

attributes.title: Table Source IP & HASSH Client & Destination IP & HASSH Server & Total Events

query.esql:
from logs-corelight.various-*
| where event.dataset == "ssh" and ssh.inferences is not null
| limit 10000
| stats count(), values(ssh.inferences) by source.ip, destination.ip
| rename source.ip as `Source IP`, destination.ip as `Destination IP`, `values(ssh.inferences)` as Inferences, `count()` as Count
| SORT Count desc
| limit 5
| keep `Source IP`, `Destination IP`, Inferences, Count

from logs-corelight.various-*
| where event.dataset == "ssh" and ssh.inferences is not null

| stats count(), values(ssh.inferences) by source.ip, destination.ip

| SORT Count desc
| limit 5
| keep `Source IP`, `Destination IP`, Inferences, Count

from logs-corelight.various-*
| where event.dataset == "ssh" and ssh.inferences is not null and ssh.host_key is not null
| limit 10000
| stats count(), values(ssh.inferences), values(ssh.host_key) by source.ip, destination.ip
| rename source.ip as `Source IP`, destination.ip as `Destination IP`, `values(ssh.inferences)` as Inferences, `values(ssh.host_key)` as `Host Key`, `count()` as Count
| SORT Count desc
| keep `Source IP`, `Destination IP`, `Host Key`, Inferences, Count
